    "yearKey": "wb-jee-2024",
    "difficulty": null
  },
  {
    "comprehension": null,
    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lh5pbcsz/cc148d9f-127b-49b3-b6e1-9b840f5309bc/36aace30-e898-11ed-8179-292e62481b94/file-1lh5pbct0.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lh5pbcsz/cc148d9f-127b-49b3-b6e1-9b840f5309bc/36aace30-e898-11ed-8179-292e62481b94/file-1lh5pbct0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"WB JEE 2023 Physics - Electronic Devices Question 7 English\"></p>\n<p>In the given circuit, find the voltage drop $$\\mathrm{V_L}$$ in the load resistance $$\\mathrm{R_L}$$.</p>",
