    "content": "What will be the current flowing through the 6k$$\\Omega $$ resistor in the circuit shown, where the breakdown voltage of the Zener is 6V?<br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l8hndrj2/9245860d-90f2-4a9e-8acf-82dada511f40/1cc8cbe0-3cfc-11ed-8d75-1fa5a7560540/file-1l8hndrj3.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l8hndrj2/9245860d-90f2-4a9e-8acf-82dada511f40/1cc8cbe0-3cfc-11ed-8d75-1fa5a7560540/file-1l8hndrj3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"WB JEE 2018 Physics - Electronic Devices Question 18 English\">",
